summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6209 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 8, Westholme Addition, being the alley between Avalon Way and 32nd Avenue Southwest from West Andover Street to West Genesee Street; and certain other alleys; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 88431, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
